e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b76ffc70959ff69abb4692510dfdf3131eef55","tid":2032714,"uid":259565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"入去檢舉佢"},{"pid":"36ecedd71ae84b91707eba72ec690d34dfacaff8","tid":2032714,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4d9d3d33e6286c22ccb64cbbab2bd2e95d9e93","tid":2032714,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"ppush"},{"pid":"9288fe0b222838aa5b40b1a09b2cde185da0cbf7","tid":2032714,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"推，屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=b7f9e95a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"2ef1901705d9208d0cbf9e3035a798df94b0ff56","tid":2032714,"uid":65813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"雖然未必有用 不過都要report"},{"pid":"73fa5136aed9077579c27ef210a9dbc06a568d5b","tid":2032714,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"條友行到時代廣場"},{"pid":"0857a6e5f78909514497ff81dad9e3390ad3b6f9","tid":2032714,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c42553c8c5489f7ba11ae703b62073dfb6c1f1b0","tid":2032714,"uid":112447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27e90e28c050fec75f14c7e90249b5d8fa05cbea","tid":2032714,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76bf86e0ec025adbdc74185556ac9f06bd4b3c3d","tid":2032714,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f460b6fcc928a3b9db007e14bbc39ce58e41a7e","tid":2032714,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fa5136aed9077579c27ef210a9dbc06a568d5b","tid":2032714,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"條友行到時代廣場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:14:41.000Z","msg":"睇路呀"},{"pid":"efe912302afa99763255f69a8e6b7e76cdf5dabd","tid":2032714,"uid":4574,"like":0,"disli